text: Farm buildings in Newbiggin Newbiggin is a tiny hamlet very close to Askrigg, North Yorkshire, England. Another Newbiggin is only about 7 miles away. The population of this parish (including Bishopdale) at the 2011 Census was 108. ==References== Category:Villages in North Yorkshire Category:Wensleydale
title: Newbiggin, Askrigg
